No. 10-156. Gene Scroggy, Warden, Petitioner v. Eugene Gall. 562 U.S. 1082, 131 S. Ct. 642, 2010 U.S. LEXIS 9133.

178 L. Ed. 2d 512,

November 29, 2010.

Motion of respondent for leave to proceed in forma pau-peris granted. Petition for writ of certio-rari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Sixth Circuit denied.

Same case below, 603 F.3d 346.
